name: Ferndale School District
notes:
2nd dose Pfizer Clinic for those who given their first doses here on 5/22. 
***Please note that due to sporting events at the school, this clinic will be held in the Cafeteria. *****

We will have some first doses available as well for anyone 12+ with a parent present if under the age of 18. If you choose to get your first vaccine here today, keep in mind that you will have to receive your second dose elsewhere. You may easily do so by using prepmod.doh.wa.org or call 1-800-525-0127 to find your second appointment. Schedule it between June 29 & July 7th and bring your vaccine card with you.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Hawker Center for Integrative Medicine - COVID Vaccine Clinic
notes: ***We provide MODERNA 1st and 2nd doses*** Please sign up for an appointment time. When you arrive to the clinic, please continue to wear your face covering, practice physical distancing and wash your hands frequently to help reduce transmission. Please arrive no more than 10 minutes prior to your appointment time. Expect to stay for 15 minutes after you receive your vaccine to monitor for any adverse reaction. Due to the limited supplies of vaccines provided to us each week, we are unable to take walk-ins, so please make an appointment. ***Directions to the Hawker Center for Integrative Medicine:*** Our clinic is located in the Hidden Valley Office Complex. 1) When you arrive at the complex, take either driveway all the way to the back of the building. 2) We are located on the prominent corner at the very back of the building and we have our own private entrance. Look for the parking lot with the number "2" in a big steel frame. Do NOT go into the main building for we have a private entrance accessible directly from the parking lot. Look for our sign with our logo in the window and a door with the number "C-102" on it, visible from the parking lot. ***Visit our website for further contact information and directions to the clinic: https://www.hawkerhealth.com/contact-us/ ***
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Yakima County Health District COVID Vaccination Site
notes:
Additional Information: ***1ST & 2nd DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS!!!!*** The
vaccination clinic will take place at Bale Breaker Brewing. This clinic will be
outside. Masks are required. Please wear clothing which allows access to your
shoulder. All individuals 12 and over are eligible to get vaccinated. Those under 18
must be accompanied by a parent/guardian or must get parental consent via
video/phone call or paper format.

La clínica de vacunación se ubicara en Bale Breaker Brewing. Se requieren
máscaras. Por favor, use ropa que permita acceso a su brazo. Todas las personas
mayores de 12 años son elegibles para vacunarse. Los menores de 18 años deben
estar acompañados por un padre/tutor o deben obtener el consentimiento de los
padres por video/llamada telefónica o en papel.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
